# For a sovereign AI expert

A platform that enables you to seamlessly communicate your knowledge and facilitates frictionless payment and delivery of models to your clients would be a game changer.

Clients would be able to pay you easily and privately through frictionless methods within the platform, with no transaction costs.

They could download your signed models as a single binary that is safe and works on every operating system, or at the very least, makes the process smooth for both them and you.

Suddenly, the business model becomes viable.

Right now, it’s hellish—trying out models for clients is labor-intensive and risky, especially in terms of configuration. If they get it wrong, it can leave their computers in a broken state.

